import FormControl from "@mui/material/FormControl";
import InputLabel from "@mui/material/InputLabel";
import { ThemeProvider, createTheme } from "@mui/material/styles";
import InputForm from "./InputForm";
import { MuiThemeMod } from "../../css/muiTheme";
import Grid from "@mui/material/Grid";
import Paper from "@mui/material/Paper";
import Button from "@mui/material/Button";
import { useState } from "react";

function ProjectForm() {
  const theme = createTheme(MuiThemeMod);

  return (
    <ThemeProvider theme={theme}>
      <form onSubmit={submitForm}>
        <Grid
          container
          spacing={3}
          justifyContent="center"
          alignItems="center"
          marginTop={2}
        >
          <Grid item xs={8} md={8} lg={10}>
            <Paper>
              <FormControl fullWidth>
                <InputLabel
                  htmlFor="my-input"
                  sx={{ color: theme.palette.primary.main }}
                >
                  Project name:
                </InputLabel>
                <InputForm
                  id="name"
                  name="name"
                  type="text"
                />
              </FormControl>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={8} md={8} lg={10}>
            <Paper>
              <FormControl fullWidth>
                <InputLabel
                  htmlFor="my-input"
                  sx={{ color: theme.palette.primary.main }}
                >
                  Email address:
                </InputLabel>
                <InputForm
                  id="email"
                  nameInput="email"
                  type="text"
                />
              </FormControl>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={8} md={8} lg={5}>
            <Paper>
              <FormControl fullWidth>
                <InputLabel
                  htmlFor="my-input"
                  sx={{ color: theme.palette.primary.main }}
                >
                  Your phone:
                </InputLabel>
                <InputForm
                  id="phone"
                  nameInput="phone"
                  type="text"
                />
              </FormControl>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={8} md={8} lg={5}>
            <Paper>
              <FormControl fullWidth>
                <InputLabel
                  htmlFor="my-input"
                  sx={{ color: theme.palette.primary.main }}
                >
                  Project budget:
                </InputLabel>
                <InputForm
                  id="budget"
                  nameInput="budget"
                  type="number"
                />
              </FormControl>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={8} md={8} lg={10}>
            <Paper>
              <FormControl fullWidth>
                <InputLabel
                  htmlFor="my-input"
                  sx={{ color: theme.palette.primary.main }}>
                  Project description:
                </InputLabel>
                <InputForm
                  id="description"
                  nameInput="description"
                  type="text"
                />
              </FormControl>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6} md={6} lg={5}>
            <Button
              variant="contained"
              color="primary"
              type="submit"
              fullWidth
              sx={{ color: theme.palette.secondary.main }}
            >
              Submit
            </Button>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </form>
    </ThemeProvider>
  );
}

export default ProjectForm;
